{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came around occasionally into the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the homes that he had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he only came for encouragement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He only came around for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't want him to know who we are, because we didn't want him-- we didn't want to expose him to the fact that we-- there was an organization that duplicated.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why throw that burden on him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you just don't speak about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So yes, I have met him, at least three or-- two or three different occasions, briefly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But never have I discussed with him or told him what I am doing or what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While he knew all along there couldn't be that many passports, because he knew how many he issued and so many more people had it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was the kind of thing that if we tell him, what about if they turn around and they torture him, and-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't-- it was best not to speak of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I met him, spoke to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very kind man, compassionate person, very calm, cool, very, very cool.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And young man, very handsome young man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was sent-- as I understand, King Gustav has given him diplomatic degree or diplomatic position.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came with just a couple knapsacks and a rolled-up blanket, because he didn't know what he was going to find in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, but he speak with such authority that he stood up against Eichmann and Eichmann respected that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, I have later on learned after the war there were other reasons, too, that he made it very clear that the Wallenberg family [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] is-- are the bankers in this country.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
